1198
01:22:25.308 --> 01:22:28.305
(siren wailing)

1199
01:22:34.980 --> 01:22:36.973
(siren wails)
- It's Lawson.

1200
01:22:37.542 --> 01:22:39.415
Lawson is the original killer.

1201
01:22:45.225 --> 01:22:48.094
I'm heading east in pursuit
on Livingston Highway.

1202
