1256
01:27:29.571 --> 01:27:33.247
That's me.
You can't stop me.

1257
01:27:34.110 --> 01:27:35.205
(gun roars)

1258
01:27:37.752 --> 01:27:40.287
(ears ringing)

1259
01:27:42.119 --> 01:27:44.184
(gun roaring)

1260
01:27:44.220 --> 01:27:46.887
(ears ringing)

1261
01:27:54.098 --> 01:27:57.029
